						               													<description>Villers-Bocage is a source book for Flames of War covering the battles over this French crossroads town from 12-16 June 1944.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It includes army lists for the forces that fought the battles, including the 101 Schwere SS-Panzerabteilung (Tiger Battalion), The Panzer Lehr division and the British 7th Armored Division.  It also includes three historical scenarios that can be played individually or linked into a mini-campaign.  The scenarios include historical orders of battle, but also include suggestions for running them with alternate forces.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Basic painting guides and historical background are included as well.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
